Apache:
* libapache2-mod-wsgi

Lighttpd:
* sudo easy_install web.py
* sudo easy_install flup
* Inside /etc/lighttpd/conf.d/fastcgi.conf:
	server.modules += ( "mod_fastcgi" )
	#Add Python server script
	fastcgi.server = ( "/inchi2image" =>
						((	"socket" =>		"/tmp/fastcgi.socket",
							"bin-path" =>	"/var/www/lighttpd/inchi2image/webapplication.py",
							"max-procs" =>	1,
							"check-local" => "disable"
						))
					 )

Testdrive:
* http://localhost:80/inchi2image/svg/InChI=1S/C3H7NO2S/c4-2(1-7)3(5)6/h2,7H,1,4H2,(H,5,6)/p+1